LLMs can reason, but they can't transact.

@xona_agent changes that by building the rails for the agentic economy.

It provides the infrastructure for agents to hold funds, discover services, and pay for them autonomously. https://t.co/f2ciAcGrBJ

our webinar on compliance for autonomous agent payments is now free to watch. 

@rodventures joined @rowlandgraus from @chainlink and Alex Kopferschmitt from @trmlabs to cover the agentic threat surface TRM is tracking, where Chainlink's ACE brings verifiable execution to agent workflows, and how ampersend enforces policy end to end with spending limits, identity, audit trails, and cross-chain observability. 

